Project Highlights
Provides a structured view of pitch performance by type and zone.
Offers customizable visualizations for baseball analytics enthusiasts.
Demonstrates practical applications of Python in sports analytics.
Future Enhancements
Automate data fetching using pybaseball.
Include more granular zone divisions (e.g., 9x9 grid).
Integrate player-specific analysis (e.g., Statcast data for specific MLB players).
